        \"summary\": \"Team Sync\",
        \"start\": \"<next_wednesday_at_2pm_ISO_8601>\",
        \"end\": \"<next_wednesday_at_2:30pm_ISO_8601>\",
        \"recurrence\": \"FREQ=WEEKLY;INTERVAL=2;BYDAY=WE;COUNT=12\",
        \"allday\": false
      }
    ]"
  }
}
```
- **Reasoning**: This call will create the recurring event every other Wednesday at 2pm for 30 minutes, starting next week, for 12 weeks. The `<calendar_name_from_step_1>` will be replaced with the actual calendar name obtained from the first step. The `<next_wednesday_at_2pm_ISO_8601>` and `<next_wednesday_at_2:30pm_ISO_8601>` will be replaced with the actual ISO 8601 date strings for the start and end times of the first occurrence.

By following these steps, the team sync event will be scheduled correctly in the specified calendar.
